data.description: You’ll love this stunning 3001 sqft, pool home located in the gated community of Hampton Park in Gateway! This 4 BD + den, 3.5 BA home features a NEW lanai screen, NEW hot water tank, NEW A/C capacitor, impact windows throughout, wood floors in the den, feature walls in the den/primary BD, board & batten in the 1/2 bath, an oversized loft, an abundance of natural lighting & crown molding. The open living space gives you a direct view outside at the sparkling private pool & privacy landscaping. The living area flows into the eat-in kitchen which boasts an expansive island, suite of stainless steel appliances, granite countertops & cabinets w/ upper crown molding. The primary BD provides gorgeous wood-like tile floors, large walk-in closet & ensuite complete w/ dual sinks & a walk-in shower. 2 BD, 1.5 BA & a den on the main floor & 1 BD, a full BA & loft on the second story complete this home! Hampton Park amenities include a community pool, exercise room, tennis courts & many more all while being conveniently located close to many dining/shopping options, RSW & Jet Blue Park! Gateway also offers the Club at Gateway where you can take advantage of flexible country club memberships!
